import React from "react";
import Home from "../../Asset/Icons/Home";
import {
  Accordion,
  AccordionButton,
  AccordionIcon,
  AccordionItem,
  AccordionPanel,
  Box,
  HStack,
  Icon,
  IconButton,
  Path,
  Row,
  Text,
} from "native-base";
import Copy from "../../Asset/Icons/Copy";
import Switch from "../../Asset/Icons/Switch";
import Form from "../../Asset/Icons/Form";
import Table from "../../Asset/Icons/Tables";
import Map from "../../Asset/Icons/Map";
import Widget from "../../Asset/Icons/Widget";
import Chart from "../../Asset/Icons/Chart";

export default function SidebarItems() {
  return (
    <Box mt={10}>
      <Accordion>
        <AccordionItem py={1}>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Home color="#5F72E4" />
              <Text pt={1} fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Dashboards
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>

        {/* new accordian */}
        <AccordionItem py={1}>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Copy color="#FB6440" />
              <Text fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Examples
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>

        {/* new accordian */}
        <AccordionItem py={1}>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Switch color="#0CCDEF" />
              <Text pt={2} fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Components
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>

        {/* new accordian */}
        <AccordionItem py={1}>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Form color="#F4A4B5" />
              <Text fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Forms
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>

        {/* new accordian */}
        <AccordionItem py={1}>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Table color="black" />
              <Text fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Tables
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>

        {/* new accordian */}
        <AccordionItem py={1}>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Map color="#5F72E4" />
              <Text fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Maps
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>
      </Accordion>

      <Row my={3} ml={3}>
        <IconButton
          icon={
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Widget color="#2DCE89" />
              <Text fontWeight={500} fontSize={14} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Widgets
              </Text>
            </HStack>
          }
        ></IconButton>
      </Row>

      <Row my={3} ml={3}>
        <IconButton
          icon={
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Chart color="#0CCDEF" />
              <Text fontWeight={500} fontSize={14} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Charts
              </Text>
            </HStack>
          }
        ></IconButton>
      </Row>

      <Row my={3} ml={3}>
        <IconButton
          icon={
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Widget color="#2DCE89" />
              <Text fontWeight={500} fontSize={14} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Widgets
              </Text>
            </HStack>
          }
        ></IconButton>
      </Row>
    </Box>
  );
}
